  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270970/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764932652\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270970/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764932652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270970/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764932652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>How about a rematch?<br><br>Try new top experiences together with this new action game, called Fight & Crush! Being in the shoes of a beginner fighter, your main mission is to beat all the world fighters in your upcoming fights! You will have a limited time for this and limited health, so take care! <br><br>Arm with courage! The moment of the big chance has come, don’t miss it. Study and analyze the enemies carefully because each of them is preparing a surprise for you. Everyone is waiting to see a new invincible fighter. But what surprise are you preparing for the others? <br><br>Game Features :<br>- Training/Arcade Mode<br>- 20 characters<br>- Multiple fights",
  "about_the_game": "How about a rematch?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTry new top experiences together with this new action game, called Fight & Crush! Being in the shoes of a beginner fighter, your main mission is to beat all the world fighters in your upcoming fights! You will have a limited time for this and limited health, so take care! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nArm with courage! The moment of the big chance has come, don’t miss it. Study and analyze the enemies carefully because each of them is preparing a surprise for you. Everyone is waiting to see a new invincible fighter. But what surprise are you preparing for the others? <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features :<br />\r\n- Training/Arcade Mode<br />\r\n- 20 characters<br />\r\n- Multiple fights",
